snippet.title: EVE Galaxy Conquest - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
From the creators of acclaimed MMO EVE Online, prepare to enter the vast cosmos of New Eden in an all new mobile 4x strategy game where intense factional warfare and diplomacy will force you to consider every decision, find allies, and outsmart your foes in a battle for seasonal supremacy. Are you ready to take command and write history?

Launching worldwide on October 29, 2024 for mobile devices. 

PRE-REGISTER NOW AND CLAIM REWARDS AT LAUNCH!
Official Website: https://www.evegalaxyconquest.com/
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ccpgames.evegalaxyconquest

FOLLOW OUR SOCIALS
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playEVEGalaxyConquest
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Galaxy_Conquest/
Discord: www.discord.gg/galaxyconquest
